text:
This will be my second time here. What a great coffee shop to have just around the corner from the downtown public library. The staff are friendly here and seem to be cheerful when taking orders from customers and when serving (: I like the coffee! The first time I had a cup
Of coffee with a shot of espresso/ kept me up and bright eyed. I have just ordered the latte (;
As far as parties..I  have tried the cinnamon type croissant which was sooo good- wish it was bigger lol. Currently enjoying the warmed ham and cheese croissant which is prefectLy flakey.
